reviewText: Well done DVD on the rapture.

Dr. Stauffer always has sound Bible teaching.  I learned a lot from this video.  The only issue I had was that one of the latches on the case wouldn't close.  But for me that is no big deal.  Anyone who wants to hear the real truth about the Tribulation should get this teaching.
Thorough review of PreTrib view.  Overwhelmed by evidence in Scripture...
lots of good food for thought. Hope he's correct!
